<br>
1)  So Absor deletes hundreds of accounts, millions of plat, and tons of ill-gotten items.  So what?  The person who pulled off this exploit still made a killing selling what plat he could while he could.<br>
<br>
2)  All the banned ill-gotten items are now out of bazaar circulation.  On the bright side, this will probably make some folks happy because now you cannot buy Plane of Time gear in bazaar any more...at least not until F&amp;F spend more time farming it.<br>
<br>
3)  The markets on all servers is now coin heavy and high-end gear light.  Expect it to take months for most prices to return to normal.  In the mean time, cinch up your belts and your coin purses.  There are going to be a lot of unhappy traders and buyers in 40+ bazaars for a while. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ainanimus>AinaNimus</A> at: 12/9/03 5:55 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=roninsenshi>RoninSenshi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia<br>Jihad on that ass!</span><br>  Posts: 2540<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/8/03 10:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5289.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HUNDREDS banned due to cheating!</span><hr size=1> Cheaters are the 5th Children. The Owned. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=125476" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.studioeternity.com/EverquestFV/Shinsig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
